  "instructions": [
    "Boil new potatoes until tender.",
    "Trim and julienne fresh kale leaves, discarding the stem.",
    "Heat sesame oil in a pan, add cumin seeds and coriander seeds. Toast for about 1 minute, stirring continuously to prevent burning.",
    "Add orange juice concentrate, coconut milk, and lime juice to the pan. Stir well until the mixture starts boiling.",
    "Stir in the boiled new potatoes and pickled vegetables. Cook for another few minutes until the sauce thickens slightly.",
    "Transfer the dish to a serving bowl and serve hot."
